Message: I don't have the ability to approve ads directly. The ad approval process usually takes between 1-2 business days. If you have any issues or need further assistance, please let me know!
Sure, I'd be happy to help! Could you please provide more details about the issue you're facing with your ads? This will help me assist you better.
can someone approve my ads now
I understand that you need your ads approved quickly. Unfortunately, I can't approve ads directly. However, I can escalate this issue to our support team for you. Would you like me to do that?
I've escalated your request to our support team. They will prioritize your ad approval and get back to you as soon as possible. If you need anything else, feel free to ask!
